{"tid":2176325,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港監察：港府歪曲法治","createTime":"2020-08-27T04:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T04:45:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6b85e19bfba4f60067277cf4e25508b6ec3c90","tid":2176325,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/QD6CNCF6MFC57F6XTTRVTMRY4U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FQD6CNCF6MFC57F6XTTRVTMRY4U%2F&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpk74BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=d29bb007\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200827%2FQD6CNCF6MFC57F6XTTRVTMRY4U%2F&h=03437764\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200827/QD6CNCF6MFC57F6XTTRVTMRY4U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n香港監察：港府歪曲法治<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8O1zoneQhI9zrRcriXqlq5t1yJk=/2214x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/OT347QOJEZB3XPC7ONFMRDXTBU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8O1zoneQhI9zrRcriXqlq5t1yJk%3D%2F2214x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FOT347QOJEZB3XPC7ONFMRDXTBU.jpg&h=57cc7c7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n羅哲斯<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨日拘捕民主黨立法會議員林卓廷及許智峯等16人，去年在元朗7.21事件遇襲的林卓廷更由「原告變被告」遭警方指涉嫌參與暴動。人權組織「香港監察」批評，警方行動進一步證明港府圖以法律手段對付民主派，同時讓暴力罪犯逍遙法外。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n懲處泛民 放生犯罪集團<br />\n<br />\n「香港監察」發表聲明，指大批反《逃犯條例》修訂的示威者，去年7月21日在元朗西鐵站，被大批懷疑是黑社會分子的白衣男子襲擊，事發片段在社交媒體及國際傳媒廣泛流傳，但香港警方超過30分鐘仍未回應市民緊急求助電話到場，。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。，這些拘捕進一步證明香港政府企圖以法律手段懲處民主派人士的立法會議員，同時為暴力襲擊的犯罪集團開脫。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。「當律政司司長和香港警察試圖以各種方式歪曲法治時，國際社會必須與香港民主派立法會議員同一陣線，迅速採取行動，包括制裁涉及侵犯人權行為的人」。<br />\n<br />\n英國保守黨下議員施志安（Iain Duncan Smith）亦有在社交網站Twitter轉載聲明，表達關注。<br />\n<br />\n事件亦引起國際傳媒關注，英國廣播公司（BBC）報道提到，兩名反對派議員被捕同時，香港警察亦被指控改寫去年示威者遇襲事件的歷史。"},{"pid":"fda68292bf4759b794b005d6a4f3d00d506f73a2","tid":2176325,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:34:01.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab4b2cd8819705f2ff04e97b27ca6d55912db66","tid":2176325,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T04:45:07.000Z","msg":"721真相求手足幫手backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新界北總區副指揮官曾正科交代及回應記者元朗721事件<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fQBzrS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fQBzrS</a>"}]}